gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">仲有DQ既準則從來冇正式講明，凈係選舉主任(或背後既人)決定</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Twitter組將所有Gphone被DQ的新聞Tweets放哂上Task3 會不斷更新 長做長有！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入 <span style=\"color: red;\">/task3</span> rt and like,, reply啦</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=6add5da4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGBO2PR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGBO2PR.png&h=8e218f11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11d0663f2dbebfd278d5add6de4428b61da1c92f","tid":1680813,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:51:06.000Z","msg":"唔好將政治帶入議會"},{"pid":"60bac072d994828462c5f86b46f50631bb4dea4a","tid":1680813,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:53:11.000Z","msg":"我們早前在Telegram成立了手足匿名搵工平台，助手足自行尋找明白其情況的本地良心僱主，幫助他們在漫長保釋（可能講緊一、兩年時間的排期）或長期夢境中，有工開有野做有糧出，同時又可以滿足保釋條件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680524</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/findagoodboss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindagoodboss&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=af84101d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/findagoodboss</a><img src=